### Pattern 2: Do/Don't Examples

```markdown
## Component Patterns

### ✅ DO: Use early returns

```tsx
function Component({ data }) {
  if (!data) return null;
  return <div>{data.name}</div>;
}
```

### ❌ DON'T: Nested conditionals

```tsx
function Component({ data }) {
  return (
    <div>
      {data && data.name && <span>{data.name}</span>}
    </div>
  );
}
```
```

